net.heroicefforts.viable.android.reg
Class RegEntry

java.lang.Object
  net.heroicefforts.viable.android.reg.RegEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Externalizable, Serializable
public class RegEntry
extends Object
implements Serializable, Externalizable

This class retains the configuration information required to instantiate a repository instance for a particular Viable client application. Data is acquired from the package manager and persisted to a database.
